Name: Tiger Tank 59 Ⅰ Super Tank
About the game: 'Tiger Tank 59 Ⅰ Super Tank' is a top-down shooting game In this game , Players need to control their tanks, through the enemy lines, break the enemy base, or defeat the enemy tanks Content up to 10 kinds of tanks up to 3 kinds of fighter up to 7 kinds of Super Heavy Tank up to 10 kinds of weapons up to 20 missions Features Main Base Artillery: The Enemy base full picture visible, no matter where the player will continue to fire. Fog of War: Players ' vision is limited by the fog of war, please be careful to move forward Super Heavy Tank: War Machine is the king on the battleground , It have heavy fire and thick armor.
